:::::::::::::::
:: VARIABLES :: ---- Set these to your desired values
:::::::::::::::
:: Rules for variables:
::  * NO quotes!                       (bad:  "c:\directory\path"       )
::  * NO trailing slashes on the path! (bad:   c:\directory\            )
